{
  "system_version": "1.0",
  "philosophy": "Each marketplace uses a 5-tone monochromatic ramp built around its signature hue. Shapes are rendered with a SOLID base + LIGHT highlight + DARK shadow + DARKEST detail/hatching, plus WHITE for shine.",
